# The Dockerfile builds only the Rust binary (it COPYs Cargo.toml, Cargo.lock,
# and rust/). Keep the build context small: exclude VCS, dependency/build trees,
# and runtime state so `docker build` does not stream them to the daemon.
.git
.github
node_modules
**/node_modules
target
**/target
.local
dist
docs
spec
tools
python
go
c
sh
typescript
*.log
*.pid
*.tmp
.venv
__pycache__
**/__pycache__
.mypy_cache
.pytest_cache
.ruff_cache
